snippet.title: Official Trailer - Ikémen Sengoku: Romances Across Time (Otome Game)
snippet.description:
You've just nabbed your dream job as a fashion designer when you're sent hurtling back in time to an alternate version of Sengoku era Japan! In a world where it takes one man to conquer a nation, do you have what it takes to conquer his heart?

Enjoy gorgeous characters voiced by some of Japan's most popular Voice Actors!
Nobunaga Oda (Voice: Tomokazu Sugita)
Masamune Date (Voice: Kazuki Kato)
Yukimura Sanada (Voice: Kensho Ono)
Ieyasu Tokugawa (Voice: Toshiki Masuda)
Hideyoshi Toyotomi (Voice: Kohsuke Toriumi)
Shingen Takeda (Voice: Yuuichiro Umehara)
Mitsuhide Akechi (Voice: Shunsuke Takeuchi)
Mitsunari Ishida (Voice: Yoshitaka Yamaya)
Kenshin Uesugi (Voice: Hiroaki Miura)
Sasuke Sarutobi (Voice: Kenji Akabane)
Kennyo (Voice: Tarusuke Shingaki)

Get more info about CYBIRD's Ikémen Series here:
Official Website: https://ikemen-series.com/
Official Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/cyikemen_en
Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CyIkemenSeries
